* 多啦A夢（''Doraemon''）
* IQ博士（''Dr. Slump''）
* 高達（''Moblie Suit Gundam''）
* 超時空要塞（''Super Dimension Fortress Macross''）

== 遊戲 ==

Arcadia 2001共發售約款遊戲。除了有特別標示開發商及發行商外，遊戲開發商及發行商分別是UA Limited及Emerson<ref name="vgcl" /><ref name="guide" /><ref name="critic1" /><ref name="critic2">{{cite web |url=http://videogamecritic.com/arcadia.htm |language=en |title=The Video Game Critic's Arcadia 2001 Reviews |publisher=The Video Game Critic |accessdate=2016-06-07 |archive-date=2016-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531120836/http://videogamecritic.com/arcadia.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/a2k1/category/999-all |language=en |title=Arcadia 2001 |publisher=GameFAQs |accessdate=2016-06-07 |archive-date=2016-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817153846/http://www.gamefaqs.com/a2k1/category/999-all |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gdatabase">{{cite web |url=http://gamesdbase.com/system-emerson_arcadia_2001.aspx |language=en |title=Emerson Arcadia 2001 |publisher=Games Database |accessdate=2016-06-10 |archive-date=2016-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727200836/http://gamesdbase.com/system-emerson_arcadia_2001.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

